The paper deals with the detection of cyber threats through the analysis of online discussions on the darkweb and social media platforms. This falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) as well as social media analysis (cs.SI) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques for analyzing text data, which could fall under the categories of software engineering (cs.SE) or natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper discusses the detection of data breaches, which could fall under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) or systems and control (cs.SY).
